permissions.name: Admin Chat
descriptions: Allows the player to use admin chat commands and functionality.

permissions.name: Admin Chat See
descriptions: Allows the player to see messages sent in admin chat by other players.

permissions.name: Afk bypass
descriptions: Allows player to bypass AFK delay when using /afk command.

permissions.name: Bypass Full Server
descriptions: This feature allows you to bypass the full server, example for vip rank.

permissions.name: Bypass Unknown Command Message
descriptions: Bypass replaced unknown command message, and keep the original message.

permissions.name: Bypass chat slowmode or disabled chat
descriptions: Allows you to bypass chat restrictions such as slowmode or disabled chat.

permissions.name: HelpOp Spy
descriptions: Allows player to see helpop messages sent by other players

permissions.name: Home teleport bypass
descriptions: Allows player to bypass home teleport time.

permissions.name: Jail Bypass
descriptions: Permission allows to bypass jail punishment

permissions.name: Near
descriptions: Allows the player to list the surrounding entities.

permissions.name: Near Glow
descriptions: Allows the player to highlight the surrounding entities with a glow effect.

permissions.name: Phantom Spawn Ignore
descriptions: Player with this permission will not spawn phantoms

permissions.name: Random Teleport
descriptions: Allows you to bypass random teleport delay.

permissions.name: Receive Updates
descriptions: Sends a message to the player when a new plugin update is available after joining the server.

permissions.name: Sleep Ignore
descriptions: Player with this permission will ignore sleep count needed to skip the night

permissions.name: Spawn teleport bypass
descriptions: Allows you to bypass spawn teleportation time

permissions.name: Sudo spy
descriptions: Allows you to spy on other players' sudo commands execution

permissions.name: Use powertools
descriptions: Allows the player to use powertools, which are items that execute commands when left/right-clicked.

permissions.name: Vanish Join
descriptions: Allows the player to join as vanished player.

permissions.name: Vanish See
descriptions: Allows the player to see vanished players.

permissions.name: Warp bypass
descriptions: Allows player to bypass warp teleport time.
